      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i'm buying my first house and my realtor keeps talking about escrow. what actually happens to my earnest money deposit while we're waiting to close? is it just sitting in a bank account or something?",
      "source": "evaluator",
      "targeted_response_start": "",
