      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get the referee part, but it still feels kinda weird having a huge chunk of my money just sitting there in someone else's hands for weeks. what happens if the deal falls through because of an inspection issue? do they just hand it back to me or is it a whole huge mess to get it out of that \"vault\" you mentioned?",
